{
  "stem": "27390.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them did, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they used to say that my father is a modern man, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He hadn't got a beard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I used to say to them, it doesn't-- he doesn't-- it doesn't grow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He doesn't have a beard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It doesn't grow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Just as a joke.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In school, when we had the, the secular lessons, we spoke Polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But otherwise, we spoke Yiddish and at home, also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And most Jews in that-- in Lodz-- I don't know about other cities-- but in Lodz, most Jews spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jews that spoke Polish at home were already assimilated Jews, which didn't keep any-- much about-- they didn't keep kosher, or-- or they didn't keep the Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Such Jews, they spoke Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wanted to assimilate and to be-- And I think, also, the reason maybe-- I mean, I wouldn't like to-- my-- from what I've learned over the years and what I've read, I think if you live in a country like England, for instance, most people, most Jews speak English at home, I'm told.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I speak-- with my wife and with my children, I speak English, because I'm living in this country and I'm happy here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't notice much antisemitism and the people are friendly, so I feel I-- I speak their language.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where in Poland, you tried to keep separate from the Poles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they didn't like us, and we didn't like them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I must say that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's my opinion.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Maybe I'm wrong.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was only a child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I thought-- I think that was a reason why we only spoke Yiddish at home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Although we knew the language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean I went to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I knew the language.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I knew how to speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
